(97265, 0, 0, 'Lord Illidan taught us to fight and to persevere. Together, we destroyed countless demons. YOU chose the coward\'s path.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57296, 0, 0, 'Kayn Sunfury to Player'),
(97265, 1, 0, 'You killed our own people! You spit in the face of our sacrifices!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57347, 0, 0, 'Kayn Sunfury to Player'),
